## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a2e7-103">De forma predeterminada, la palabra clave de ayuda para una clase viene dado por la <xref:System.Type.FullName%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> valor de propiedad.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a2e7-103">By default, the Help keyword for a class is given by the <xref:System.Type.FullName%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3a2e7-104">Para los miembros, palabra clave de ayuda se proporciona por el nombre completo del tipo que declara la propiedad, además del nombre de la propiedad.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a2e7-104">For members, the Help keyword is given by the full name of the type that declared the property, plus the property name itself.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a2e7-105">Por ejemplo, considere la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> propiedad en el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> control.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a2e7-105">For example, consider the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> control.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3a2e7-106">La palabra clave class es "System.Windows.Forms.Button", pero la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> palabra clave de la propiedad es "System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text", porque el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> propiedad se declara en el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control?displayProperty=nameWithType> (clase), en lugar de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> propia clase ; la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> clase hereda la propiedad.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a2e7-106">The class keyword is "System.Windows.Forms.Button", but the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property keyword is "System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text", because the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property is declared on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control?displayProperty=nameWithType> class, rather than the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> class itself; the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> class inherits the property.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a2e7-107">Por el contrario, el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> propiedad se declara en el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> clase, por lo que su palabra clave es "System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a2e7-107">By contrast, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property is declared on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> class, so its keyword is "System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult".</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a2e7-108">Cuando el sistema de ayuda Obtiene las palabras clave, buscará primero en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a2e7-108">When the Help system gets the keywords, it will first look at <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3a2e7-109">En el nivel de clase, devolverá la cadena especificada por el <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a2e7-109">At the class level, it will return the string specified by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3a2e7-110">No se usará para los miembros del tipo en cuestión, que todavía reflejará el nombre completo real del tipo declarativo, más el nombre de miembro.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a2e7-110">This will not be used for members of the type in question, which will still reflect the declaring type's actual full name, plus the member name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3a2e7-111">Este atributo admite clases fuertemente tipadas que tienen asociados documentación común pero distintos identificadores de ayuda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a2e7-111">This attribute supports strongly typed classes that have associated common documentation but distinct Help IDs.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="3a2e7-112">En el ejemplo de código siguiente se muestra cómo invalidar este comportamiento del sistema de ayuda colocando el atributo en el propio miembro.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a2e7-112">The following code example shows how to override this Help system behavior by placing the attribute on the member itself.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3a2e7-113">Estas son las palabras clave para la siguiente clase, denominada `DemoComponent`:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a2e7-113">These are the keywords for the following class, called `DemoComponent`:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="3a2e7-114">Palabra clave class: "`System.ComponentModel.Component`" (`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent`)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a2e7-114">Class keyword: "`System.ComponentModel.Component`" (`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent`)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="3a2e7-115">Palabra clave de Property1: "`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent.Property1`" (valor predeterminado)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a2e7-115">Property1 keyword: "`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent.Property1`" (default)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="3a2e7-116">Palabra clave de Property2: "`SomeNamespace.SomeOtherClass.Property2`" (`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent.Property2`)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3a2e7-116">Property2 keyword: "`SomeNamespace.SomeOtherClass.Property2`" (`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent.Property2`)</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
[HelpKeywordAttribute(typeof(Component))]  
public class DemoComponent : Component  
{  
    public string Property1  
    {  
        get  
        {  
            return "";  
        }  
    }  
  
    [HelpKeywordAttribute("SomeNamespace.SomeOtherClass.Property2")]  
    public string Property2  
    {  
        get  
        {  
            return "";  
        }  
    }  
}  
```  
  
